<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَاضْرِبْ بِسَيْفِ الْوَحْيِ كُلَّ مُعَطِّلٍ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>ضَرْبَ الْمُجَاهِدِ فَوْقَ كُلِّ بَنَانِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَاحْمِلْ بِعَزْمِ الصِّدْقِ حَملَةَ مُخُلِصٍ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>مُتَجَرِّدٍ للهِ غَيرِ جَبَانِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَاثبُْتْ بِصَبْرِكَ تَحْتَ أَلْوِيةِ الْهُدَى<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَإِذَا أَصِبْتَ فَفِي رِضَا الرَّحْمَنِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَاجْعَلْ كِتَابَ اللهِ وَالسُّنَنَ الَّتِي<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>ثَبَتَتْ سِلاَحَكَ ثُمَّ صِحْ بِجَنَانِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>مَنْ ذَا يُبَارِزُ فَلْيُقَدِّم نَفْسَهُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>أَوْ مَنْ يُسَابِقُ يَبْدُ فِي الْمِيدَانِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَاصْدَعْ بِمَا قَالَ الرَّسُولُ وَلا تَخَفْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>مِنْ قِلَّةِ الأَنْصَارِ وَالأَعْوَانِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فَاللهُ نَاصِرُ دِينِهِ وَكِتَابِهِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَاللهُ كَافٍ عَبْدَهُ بأمَانِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>لا تَخشَ مِن كَيدِ العدُوِّ وَمكْرِهِم<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فَقِتَالُهُمْ بِالْكِذْبِ والْبُهتَانِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَجُنُودُ أتبَاعِ الرَّسُولِ مَلاَئِكٌ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَجُنُودُهُمْ فَعَسَاكِرُ الشَّيطانِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>شَتَّانَ بينَ العَسْكَرَيْنِ فَمَنْ يَكُنْ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>مُتَحَيِّزًا فَلَيْنُظُرِ الْفِئَتَانِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>